title: Bangla Newspaper
description:
Read Bangla newspapers in one app. Various newspapers from Bangladesh and West Bengal are available.
Newspapers includes:
Anandabazar Patrika, Bartaman, Ganashakti, Sangbad Pratidin, Aajkaal, Telegraph, Statesman, Century Sangbad, Ebela, Ei SamayIttefaq, Prothom Alo, Kaler Kantho, Jugantor, ManabZamin, Amar Desh, Shamokal, Amader Shomoy, Janakantha, Inqilab, Bhorer Kagoj, Sangbad, Dinkal, Noya Diganta, Sangram, Jai Jai Din, Manobkantha, Bangladesh Protidin, Destiny
etc
